OL,3,CLong Covid 'leaves traces in the
OL,4,Cblood' that could lead to successful
OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FLong leaves telltale signs in the
OL,8,Fblood which could pave the way for
OL,9,Ftargeted treatment, new research
OL,10,Fsuggests.
OL,12,FFindings from the largest UK study of
OL,13,Fpatients admitted to hospital with
OL,14,Fcoronavirus show that long Covid leads
OL,15,Fto ongoing inflammation which can be
OL,16,Fdetected in the blood.
OL,18,FRoughly one in ten Covid infections
OL,19,Flead to long Covid with an estimated
OL,20,F65 million people suffering from it
OL,21,Faround the world.
