OL,3,CLong Covid 'leaves traces in the
OL,4,Cblood' that could lead to successful
OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FDespite extensive research into the
OL,8,Fissue the medical world still has few
OL,9,Fdirect treatments for long Covid, with
OL,10,Fmost remedies based on specific
OL,11,Fsymptoms the patient is suffering like
OL,12,Ffatigue or brain fog rather than
OL,13,Ftackling the root cause.
OL,15,FIn an analysis of more than 650 people
OL,16,Fwho had been in hospital with severe
OL,17,FCovid-19, patients with prolonged
OL,18,Fsymptoms showed evidence of their
OL,19,Fimmune system being activated.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/9
