OL,3,CLong Covid 'leaves traces in the
OL,4,Cblood' that could lead to successful
OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FHe said the study contains a "hopeful
OL,8,Fmessage which says that there are
OL,9,Fthese biological pathways that are
OL,10,Factivated from different forms of
OL,11,Fpersistent symptomatology after Covid,
OL,12,Fand people aren't imagining it.
OL,14,F"It's something which is genuinely
OL,15,Fhappening to them.
OL,17,F"A lot of the symptoms do ultimately
OL,18,Fresolve and we're continuing this
OL,19,Fstudy and looking at later time
OL,20,Fpoints."
