OL,3,CLong Covid 'leaves traces in the
OL,4,Cblood' that could lead to successful
OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FThe study, published in the journal
OL,8,FNature Immunology, is the latest
OL,9,Fresearch from two collaborative
OL,10,Fgroups, PHOSP-Covid and ISARIC-4C.
OL,12,FThese involve scientists and
OL,13,Fclinicians from Imperial alongside
OL,14,Fcollaborators from the Universities of
OL,15,FLeicester, Edinburgh and Liverpool
OL,16,Famong others and funded by UK Research
OL,17,Fand Innovation (UKRI) and the National
OL,18,FInstitute for Health and Care Research
OL,19,F(NIHR).
