OL,3,CLong Covid 'leaves traces in the
OL,4,Cblood' that could lead to successful
OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FIn the latest study, researchers
OL,8,Fincluded 426 people who were
OL,9,Fexperiencing symptoms consistent with
OL,10,Flong Covid ` having been admitted to
OL,11,Fhospital with Covid-19 at least six
OL,12,Fmonths prior to the study.
OL,14,FThey were compared with 233 people who
OL,15,Fwere also admitted for Covid-19 but
OL,16,Fwho had fully recovered.
OL,18,FSamples of blood plasma were taken and
OL,19,Fa total of 368 proteins known to be
OL,20,Finvolved in inflammation and immune
OL,21,Fsystem modulation were measured.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/9
