OL,3,CLong Covid 'leaves traces in the
OL,4,Cblood' that could lead to successful
OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FResearchers found that, compared to
OL,8,Fpatients who had fully recovered,
OL,9,Fthose with long Covid showed a pattern
OL,10,Fof immune system activation indicating
OL,11,Finflammation of myeloid cells and
OL,12,Factivation of a family of immune
OL,13,Fsystem proteins called the complement
OL,14,Fsystem.
OL,16,FMyeloid cells are formed in the bone
OL,17,Fmarrow and produce various types of
OL,18,Fwhite blood cells that circulate in
OL,19,Fthe blood and migrate into organs and
OL,20,Ftissues where they respond to damage
OL,21,Fand infection.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/9
